Recommends:
 firefox (>= 67) | firefox-esr (>= 67) | chromium (>= 69.0.3497.100)
Description: Browser extension to store web site credentials in KeePassXC
 KeePassXC-Browser is a web browser extension for Firefox and Chromium that
 connects to the password manager KeePassXC. It allows one to store and retrieve
 credentials for web site in/from KeePassXC. See package keepassxc for its
 description.
 .
 Please note that KeePassXC must not only be running, but also be configured
 accordingly for this extension to work!
